==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Godspeed
<hw>God"speed`</hw> <pr>(g⟦ocr⟧d"sp⟦emac⟧d`)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<def>Success; prosperous journeying; -- a contraction of the phrase,
⟦ldquo⟧<xex>God speed</xex> you.⟦rdquo⟧ </def> <altsp>[Written also as
two separate words.]</altsp>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Receive him not into house, neither bid him <qex>God
speed</qex>.</q> <rj><qau>2 John 10.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Godward</ent>⟦br⟧
